basic.blooming: Flowering period March-May, fruiting period July-August
basic.color: Flower color yellow, golden yellow, with dark red dots inside

maintenance.soil: Soil with loose texture or soil with specific nutrients
maintenance.sunlight: Like sunshine, resistant to half shade, avoid strong direct light

maintenance.pruning: Remove aged tissues, dead, rotten, diseased leaves timely
